thread.title: Jennifer Timbs

author: Jennifer Timbs
title: Jennifer Timbs
text:
We here at No Bugs have been 20 years in business of Insect manufacturing both Australia, Canada, USA and China, we have been very successful until all the copies of our great product took over 90% of our business built after Sydney Olympics.
We have suffered with the right cash flow providers. On Deck have gone beyond excellence and helped us to get carry on finance for our low income during the winter, got us to the peak season ( now ) and supported us with enough money to manufacture a container, save a lot of money and increased our profit margins. Good on On deck when the Government and financial institutions have their head in the sands not trying to help small business survive or re grow.
